# Universal Language Puzzles & Rituals (2025-06-04)

## Purpose
- Gate anchor creation/restoration and advanced magic actions behind skill-based puzzles
- Teach and reinforce Universal Language concepts (symbols, logic, harmony, etc.)
- Provide narrative and gameplay consequences for puzzle success/failure

## Puzzle Types
- Symbol alignment and decoding
- Logic and pattern recognition
- Sequence crafting (rituals)
- Sound/melody puzzles
- Emotional intelligence and harmony puzzles

## Integration
- Puzzle UI/modal appears on anchor actions
- Modding hooks for new puzzle types and difficulty
- Tied to Timestream and world state (puzzle difficulty or type may change based on timeline)
